.TH wsp-group 1  "group " 
.SH NAME
group \- Manage repo groups (deprecated, use `wsp template`)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBgroup\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage repo groups (deprecated, use `wsp template`)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
group\-new(1)
Create a new repo group
.TP
group\-ls(1)
List all groups [read\-only]
.TP
group\-show(1)
Show repos in a group [read\-only]
.TP
group\-rm(1)
Remove a group
.TP
group\-update(1)
Add or remove repos from a group
.TP
group\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
